blocks.text:
205.1 Purpose. Task 205 is to perform and document a System Hazard Analysis (SHA) to 
verify system compliance with requirements to eliminate hazards or reduce the associated risks; 
to identify previously unidentified hazards associated with the subsystem interfaces and faults; 
identify hazards associated with the integrated system design, including software and subsystem 
interfaces; and to recommend actions necessary to eliminate identified hazards or mitigate their 
associated risks.

